HB 221 Original 2026 Regular Session Echols
Designates the new Mississippi River bridge connecting La. Hwy. 1 to La. Hwy. 30 as the
"President Donald J. Trump Expressway".
Directs the Dept. of Transportation and Development (DOTD) to erect and maintain
appropriate signage reflecting this designation once the bridge is constructed, provided local
or private monies are received by the DOTD equal to its actual cost for material, fabrication,
mounting posts, and installation of the signage, not to exceed the sum of $750 per sign.
